Vim dream
=========

An originate color scheme for vim. 

Install
-------

[Vundle](https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim)

    Plugin 'crusoexia/vim-dream'

Usage
-----

_Dream:_

    colorscheme dream

Configuration
-------------

* Italic

If your font support italic, to enable the it, use:

    let g:dream_italic = 1

Javascript
----------

Works better with [vim-javascript](https://github.com/pangloss/vim-javascript), which provide features such as param syntax highlight.

